                <p facs="#facs_1_r1">
                    <lb n="N001" />Durchleüchtiger Fürst, herzall<choice>
                        <expan />
                        <abbr>e</abbr>
                    </choice>r<choice>
                        <expan />
                        <abbr>l</abbr>
                    </choice>i<choice>
                        <expan />
                        <abbr>e</abbr>
                    </choice>bster <choice>
                        <expan>herr</expan>
                        <abbr>h</abbr>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <expan>vatter</expan>
                        <abbr>v</abbr>
                    </choice>
                    <lb n="N002" />                        
                        Weil villeicht der Weikh dem curir möcht
                    <lb n="N003" />vohrkommen, also hab durch diße zeilen <choice>
                        <expan>vnterdehnigst</expan>
                        <abbr>vt</abbr>
                    </choice>
                    <lb n="N004" />aufwarten wollen. Ewer Durchlaucht werden vom Deütsch<choice>
                        <expan />
                        <abbr>me</abbr>
                    </choice>ist<choice>
                        <expan />
                        <abbr>er</abbr>
                    </choice>
                    <lb n="N005" />                        
                        selbsten vernemmen, wie gott vns Offen
                    <lb n="N006" />geschenkt hatt. Befehl mich <choice>
                        <expan>vnterdehnigst</expan>
                        <abbr>vd</abbr>
                    </choice>
                    <lb n="N007" />                        
                        ewer Durchlaucht
                    <lb n="N008" />
                    <choice>
                        <expan>vnterdehnigste</expan>
                        <abbr>vnt</abbr>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <expan>trewgehorsamste</expan>
                        <abbr>trewgehos</abbr>
                    </choice> do<supplied>c</supplied>                        
                        hter
                    <lb n="N009" />                        
                        EMT
                    <lb n="N010" />Wien den 4ten <choice>
                        <expan>septembris</expan>
                        <abbr>7br</abbr>
                    </choice>                        
                        1686
                    </p>
                </div>
            </body>
